title: Episode 11: The Issue with the Tissue
itunes:title: Episode 11: The Issue with the Tissue
description:
Bonus Belly!

Bobby rejects the science of eating poop.

Khalyla confronts a mortifying possibility of sibling love.

We fan out out old flames, show you how to exercise your penis in a crossfit kinda way, and teach you how to deflect the teachings of L. Ron Hubbard. 

 

Recorded October 29, 2015

Music by Bobby Lee

Instagram: @tigerbelly

Twitter: @thetigerbelly
